description: This file 'CosaCM.cpp' is a C++ source file implementing a class 'CosaCM' with methods to interact with cable modem (CM) related functionalities, including getting and setting configurations, retrieving status, and managing diagnostic data. It also includes external C function declarations for various hardware and system interactions related to DOCSIS, DHCP, and channel info.
